{"tid":59402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視英超播放權暫至1月3日","createTime":"2016-12-29T15:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T16:38:38.000Z","uid":12575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37360e5404f23c3891753d85ea49045d03daa299","tid":59402,"uid":12575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"有用戶發現樂視體育在 26 日的英超比賽直播，到下半場時訊號中斷，令人懷疑樂視能否繼續轉播賽事。<br />\n擁有英超轉播權的新英體育指，當晚沒有暫停給樂視的播放訊號，但該公司透露，和樂視已達成新的還款備忘。<br />\n目前樂視所支付的版權費尾數，只足夠把播放權延續到 1 月 3 日，之後能否繼續將會成為疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DPAGES_TIMELINE%26fref%3Dnf&d=HJ3VHFVOi4atUZKNgWQtTHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=88d88f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE&amp;fref=nf</a>"},{"pid":"03016cd4e42af663012806f82e04cd715dbd5093","tid":59402,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d1f66f8cac5d4228c38fdc109b5271074cf67d","tid":59402,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"還有党"},{"pid":"945d19feceebeea428f77e9aac2f16ea716d3a9a","tid":59402,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4a7ac0dbe6